## Baseline Validation

Before optimising, run one baseline evaluation and log it in `evals/results.tsv`.

## Iteration Loop

When iterating, follow a disciplined loop:
1. Change one dominant variable per iteration.
2. Re-run evaluations.
3. Mark the attempt as `keep` or `discard`.
4. If the run crashes, log the failure and revert to last known-good state.

